high_descs: Head towards the left side of the kitchen sink counter on the right.
Pick up the knife sitting on the counter, to the left of the sink.
Turn left and head towards the small brown table on the right, to the left of the sink counter.
Cut the red fruit on top of the small brown table.
Turn around and head towards the white table on the right, which has a loaf of bread on it.
Place the knife on top of the loaf of bread.
Turn to the right and head back to the small brown table.
Pick up a slice of the red fruit.
Turn around and head towards the microwave oven against the wall.
Place the fruit in the microwave, heat it, and take it out.
Turn around and head back to the small brown table.
Place the slice of fruit on the small brown table.
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of fruit and heat it.

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter top to the left side of the sink.
Pick the knife up from the counter top.
Take a step to the left with the knife.
Slice the apple sitting behind the soap dispenser on the small black table.
Turn to the left and face the white table.
Set the knife down on top of the bread on the table.
Turn back to face the sliced apple.
Pick up a piece of the apple from the table.
Bring the apple with you and go face the black microwave on the other side of the kitchen.
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it, and then take it back out.
Bring the apple slice with you and go back to where you sliced it on the black table.
Put the apple slice down in front of the soap dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of cooked apple on the table.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Move to the left to face the end table.
Slice the tomato on the end table.
Turn around and go to the table behind you.
Set the butter knife on the table.
Turn around and go back to the end table behind you.
Pick up a tomato slice on the end table.
Go across the room to the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave.
Turn around and go to the end table across the room.
Set the hot tomato slice on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato slice on the end table.
